{"tid":1422070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有一刻懷疑過既人入黎","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:11:03.000Z","uid":77148,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bd28e4f532c512eeaf43091704fca6526c915c36","tid":1422070,"uid":77148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:43:39.000Z","msg":"身邊有好多事不關己既港豬<br />\n藍色父母，親戚，同事，五毛<br />\n佢地班地平說總會有自己既原因去屌我地<br />\n有d講到好撚有道理咁<br />\n加上大量五毛分化<br />\n但一定要好好思考每一個post，每一個看似有道理既言論<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千萬唔可以比敵人帶風向！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港就係靠我地！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地唔可以比敵人動搖！</span><br />\n就算有唔同聲音，唔同意見<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">永不割席！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有手足同家人反面，比公司炒，同朋友絕交<br />\n看盡人性既醜惡<br />\n當你感到悲痛，無助，甚至懷疑人生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定唔好忘記有一大班手足一齊努力！<br />\n你仲有我地依個大家庭！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">撐主呀咁多位手足！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放核彈都唔撚割！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"2e731799f9253130d506cdeb7b60242907bf4ae7","tid":1422070,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:44:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c344f7ebb121b5a76e75c1ef1f3405405a626d67","tid":1422070,"uid":238346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"乜撚都唔割"},{"pid":"9483e49455e29f69d70e32983702d90d149bf22d","tid":1422070,"uid":77148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放核彈都唔撚割！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b4c3f68c324050eec4cdc057c36a5116811b79b","tid":1422070,"uid":77148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"